<section>
  <div class="md:max-w-md md:mx-auto mx-6 pb-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Voting for the Student Council</h1>
    <p class="font-medium">Term starting April 2025</p>
    <div class="my-4 bg-slate-300 rounded-md p-4">
      <ul class="list-disc pl-4">
        <li>Voting is open from 17/03 and closes on 23/03.</li>
        <li>Every vote is anonymous.</li>
        <li>You can only vote once.</li>
        <li>If you are in favor of a candidate, vote YES.</li>
        <li>If you are against a candidate, vote NO.</li>
        <li>If you are unsure or indifferent about a candidate, choose ABSTAIN.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="max-w-md mx-auto pb-12">
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { vote: @vote } %>
  </div>
</section>
